of its leadership

53
00:02:15,940 --> 00:02:19,120
at or above the senior vice president level.”

54
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:21,360
OK, so it fired a few people.

55
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:22,360
No big deal.

56
