99
00:04:06,690 --> 00:04:09,610
And now, off the roads and into the sea.

100
00:04:09,610 --> 00:04:11,520
The South China Sea.

101
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:13,110
Where Filipino fishermen are accusing

102
